498369356be0b411f0481","tid":561781,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"[size=6][red][b]<br />\n咪就係呀蛆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係key 圖嚟㗎, 真係明荃BB嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/064330_15d031012603c9dd22da6f46626ae6a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F064330_15d031012603c9dd22da6f46626ae6a8.jpg&h=d5457ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿蛆繼上次五十週年盛宴再度穿上黑色deep v 晚裝坦露酥胸<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/070236_3fb257b3490667540f700dc64614c247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F070236_3fb257b3490667540f700dc64614c247.jpg&h=43c9c3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/070236_efbfdd52b91600fb3ec8181ffbb76381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F070236_efbfdd52b91600fb3ec8181ffbb76381.jpg&h=7f1f9b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢輯相重望落有啲似AV 女優添<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/175844_e973fcab8b910bdeb887e10a812f964e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F175844_e973fcab8b910bdeb887e10a812f964e.jpg&h=140e9643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重溫呀蛆嘅deep v<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(遮住唔畀你班鹹濕連登仔睇蝕哂!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/070358_11636352a0dfa83953ef167dbb899f49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F070358_11636352a0dfa83953ef167dbb899f49.gif&h=cc877285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以細心啲睇多次<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/070133_f293b4522b7432ace6b9e1beac83847b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F070133_f293b4522b7432ace6b9e1beac83847b.jpg&h=433501a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來阿蛆嘅deep V 比上次更低，差唔多deep 到落肚臍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怪得引到班慈善星輝淫濟夜嘅CEO 趨之若鶩向汪氏諮詢諮詢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/070727_8637b1e05e45675c0c025f2157cd72c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F070727_8637b1e05e45675c0c025f2157cd